WEBVTT

00:02.847 --> 00:06.149
(Zedd)
<i>Richard Cypher,</i>
<i>you are the true Seeker.</i>

00:06.150 --> 00:09.718
( <i>heroic theme playing</i> )

00:09.728 --> 00:14.628
